00:13:20.459 --> 00:13:27.730
Flame is not an end-user application. It is
an Algorithm and API, but a departure from

00:13:27.730 --> 00:13:33.670
the usual Graphics APIs, which are based on
the metaphors of the pen geometry in 3D. Flame

00:13:33.670 --> 00:13:37.720
images are formed by solving a recursive equation
with thousands of parameters and millions

00:13:37.720 --> 00:13:43.670
of variables. The results are distinctive,
recognizable, and extremely diverse.

00:13:43.670 --> 00:13:49.019
How do designers make Flame images? At first,
they used Flame plugins, made by other programmers,

00:13:49.019 --> 00:13:54.100
