GIMP. Eventually, more powerful standalone

00:13:58.739 --> 00:14:05.559
apps appeared, including Apotheosis in 2004,
Oxidizer for Mac in 2006, Cosmic for LINUX

00:14:05.559 --> 00:14:13.459
in 2008, Apple 3D in 2009 and the cross-platform
Frost in 2009. Following Flame's open-source

00:14:13.459 --> 00:14:17.709
GPL licensing, these applications are all
also GPL.

00:14:17.709 --> 00:14:24.059
